OL,3,CMadeleine McCann suspect appears in
OL,4,Ccourt for separate sex attacks
OL,6,FOn Friday, the man who remains the
OL,7,Fprime suspect in the disappearance of
OL,8,Fthree-year-old Madeleine, appeared in
OL,9,Fcourt in Brunswick, Germany.
OL,11,FDressed in a suit while handcuffed, it
OL,12,Fis the first time Brueckner has been
OL,13,Fseen in public since being linked to
OL,14,Fthe McCann case.
OL,16,FAfter the short hearing, Judge
OL,17,FChristina Engelmann adjourned the case
OL,18,Funtil next Friday so that a
OL,19,Freplacement lay judge can be found.
