OL,6,FIt was during the investigation into
OL,7,Fthe other attacks in the Algarve that
OL,8,FGerman prosecutors began to
OL,9,Finvestigate Brueckner for Madeleine
OL,10,FMcCann's abduction.
OL,12,FProsecutor Hans Christian Wolters,
OL,13,Fnamed him as the prime suspect and
OL,14,Fbelieves Madeleine is no longer alive.
OL,16,FBrueckner denies all the charges
OL,17,Fagainst him and denies any involvement
OL,18,Fin Madeleine's disappearance.
